<TD ALIGN="left" VALIGN="top" CLASS="pn-normal">
<b>Topic</b> <a href="search.php?query=&amp;topic=5&amp;author=">IB Guild Raids</a><br>
After much messing around figuring out how best to pull this guy, we finally pulled it off.  We were able to do it with just 10 people.<br />
<br />
Xi Thall isn't that difficult a fight but getting him out of his little lakehouse where everything HTs isn't too pleasant.  And his own personal 1,001 point HT does put a damper on anyone's day.<BR><BR><div align="center"><b>Xi Thall's drop:</b><br />
Idol of the Fallen [Necreia]<br />
<br />
<img src="http://www.insidiousblood.net/storypics/17/idolofthefallen.gif"><br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.insidiousblood.net/storypics/17/xithall.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.insidiousblood.net/storypics/17/xithall_tn.jpg"></a><br />
<br />
And for the most devasting example of the new advancement point system, I give you this:<br />
<br />
<img src="http://www.insidiousblood.net/storypics/17/criticalblast3.gif"></div> <br><br>

</TD>
</TR>
